commit.message:
Fixed Issue #3

- Users can now like/dislike notes from others and can view the like
count.

Fixed issue #12

- Users can now delete notes they have created.

Fix for Issue #4

- Added controllers and jdbctemplate to handle note edits.

Major Feature Corrections #1

- added courselist to user's feed for dropdown
- handled missing session redirections
- notes which are not approved moved to separate tab on user's feed
- removed unused declarations
- fixed navigation UI with icons
- edit button opens a modal to edit
- contents of notes are collapsed by default, view button shows content
- fixed My Courses and My Friends pages to show note and student cards
- added options to create both image and text type notes
- removed MySQL connections warnings for SSL certificates
Fixed API Key for Microsoft Computer Vision.
